channel.title: Terraria: Underground Theme Remix - BobTheGUYYYYY [techno, remix]
channel.description:
I made another music! I’ve loved terraria for a while and I’m working on committing to shorter tracks so I can lower my personal standards (which are a little too high atm, considering I can barely release a track per month or something)
Anyways! Here it is. I hope you enjoy!
[![image|500x500](upload://peoTF3aWA6EmsQqcOA46A9TDhgh.png)](https://soundcloud.com/bobtheguyyyyy/terraria-underground-theme)
<small>mine that cover art with a shroomite digging claw</small>
